title: ULTRAVIOLET - Re/Invented (Songs between 2004/2008) (2008)
description:
ULTRAVIOLET - Re/Invented (Songs between 2004/2008) (2008)

Ultraviolet latest album is "Re/invented", a collection of songs between 2004/2008. Includes every B-side released, rarities and new versions. After 3 studio albums and 2 singles, ultraviolet wants to take a break and look behind 4 years of work, 4 years of songs and feelings. This is a rearviewmirror in the career of ultraviolet.

This album is free for downloading, so enjoy it.
